Afọ Ọmụmụ  -  4 Epurel 1959 (afọ iri isii n'otu)
Rufina Ubah (nke a na-asụpe kwa Uba; amụrụ n'abali anọ n'onwa epurel n'afọ 1959) bụ onye Naijiria na-agbabu ọsọ, onye pụrụ iche na ọsọ 100 metres.
Ubah gbara onye nke anọ na 4 x 100 metres relay na 1991 World Championships, tinyere ya na ndị otu ya Beatrice Utondu, Christy Opara-Thompson na Mary Onyali-Omagbemi.
Na nke onye, Ubah ritere medaal oze na 1991 All-Africa Games
